Package: spectrace
Type: Package
Title: Functions for importing and processing raw Spectrace output
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Steffen Hartmeyer
Maintainer: Steffen Hartmeyer <steffen.hartmeyer@epfl.ch>
Description: This package provides functions for importing the raw CSV output 
    files from Spectrace into R and for processing this data to derive advanced
    metrological quantities.
